{"type": "article", "id": 22696, "title": "“意面几何学”包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-23T07:30:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 50, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607104155w1Ah0uBWrtGKix3U.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">Geometry of Pasta 是由平面设计师 Caz Hildebrand 和主厨 Jacob Kenedy 一起创立的意面品牌，他们在 2010 年一起推出了一本关于烹饪的书。他们充分开发意大利面的各种形状设计出黑白两色的图案，在果酱和意面的包装上都体现出这种具有很强装饰感的“意面的几何学”。盒装意面中间开了一个小窗口，可以看到意面的形态，<a href=\"http://www.geometryofpasta.com/\">他们的网站里有详细的介绍和购买途径。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104152EnimMfIohCr7HVv4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104153EZt4lLa5JMqTYB8U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104153cH0xaM2ntPFZ1iY7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104154n7W4a5cyU9VTBZFq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104154fi8aLMktRF3SwZ5u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071041551LriytsAl28BvGIY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}